876
01:03:18,000 --> 01:03:19,000
 Mjerodavni to znaju.

877
01:03:19,000 --> 01:03:20,000
 Dobro.

878
01:03:20,000 --> 01:03:21,000
 Da ga ja imam.

879
01:03:21,000 --> 01:03:22,000
 Oblično.

880
01:03:22,000 --> 01:03:25,000
 I ja predlažem za sto godina, kad ga naprave,

881
01:03:25,000 --> 01:03:28,000
